<br>
  Because i like to roleplay my gnome magician alot, and most of the time when i cant find no group or i'm bored out of my wazzoo. I'll mem that spell and starts summoning monsters !!!  <br>
<br>
   I've seen some monsters that i was just GASPING !!!  i remember one in Skyfire, man it looooked sooo nice. Being level 38 at the time... I didnt want to zone back to OT.. hehe<br>
<br>
   But the best silly prank i pulled was this.. 1 day in Oasis , i was bored and decided to pull out my level 34 summon monster spell.. I was near the Orc highway and the pet gave me a FIRE Sand giant.. heheh Then i got this idea <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  .. Cast expedience on my pet and Burnout 2. Then make a run towards the dock, shouting..  SAND GIANT to dock !!!!   heheh you guys should of seen how fast dock cleared up and people shouting...  DONT PULL THE SANG GIANT TO DOCK YOU sfdlkslkfdflkm !!   When i got to dock, no one was even near.. hehe i sat down, right clicked on my Pegasus cloak, and waited..  A few shouts went.  SAND GIANT AT THE DOCK...  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Then finnally someone realised that the SG at the dock was a pet.. :P  hehe. But was this fun !!!!!  <br>
<br>
  But for soloing, i'd never pop up a monster for a fight, for the simple reason that me being level 40 i can summon very more powerful elementals with Focus items !!  Thus me being evle 40 i dont know about the level 50 monsters, but at my level the only time i'd use it would be in a group where my pet aint a big factor. For example Dreadlands, was in a group yesterday that usually toook mobs down faster than you can say.. Fazzy Wabbithugger.<br>
<br>
  But in all, i like this spell as it's something to see other than your 4 types of pets, but i never could figure out how i could summon a Ice orc in Oasis !! <br>
<br>
