<br>
What i was refferring to was Monster Summoning 2, which can be quite efficiant for hunting through level 54 at least (when you get the rogue pet.... /drool  maybe i should start leveling again...) and not sure how far from there...<br>
<br>
I just wanted to let people know that Monster summon actually has practical uses, even if it may not have been intended that way.<br>
<br>
Right now, i'd rather use a monster summoning 2 pet than any other for group OR solo.<br>
